<m0>Hollybrook golf club gives hospital<ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS 1.26 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>money for cardiac monitoring device<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 2 IS .22 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
